
# Phase 5 Testing Plan — Complete Integration & RAG Upload Testing

## Overview

This document outlines the comprehensive testing required to close out Phase 5: Integration Testing & Migration. All tests must be executed with **real Azure resources** (Azure Functions, Storage Queues, Supabase) to validate the complete worker-queue architecture and RAG upload pipeline.

**Related Documentation**:
- **Deployment Guide**: `phase_5_azure_functions_deployment.md` - Complete Azure Functions deployment instructions
