## Prerequisites

Before starting testing, ensure:
- [ ] Database migrations 0019 and 0020 applied to production Supabase (see `phase_5_migration_guide.md`)
- [ ] Azure Function App `func-raglab-uploadworkers` deployed and running (see `phase_5_azure_functions_deployment.md`)
- [ ] All four worker functions deployed: `ingestion-worker`, `chunking-worker`, `embedding-worker`, `indexing-worker`
- [ ] Environment variables configured in Function App (see `../../setup/environment_variables.md`)
- [ ] Application Insights monitoring enabled
- [ ] Azure Storage Queues accessible (`raglabqueues` storage account)
- [ ] Test PDF available: `docs/inputs/scan_classic_hmo.pdf` (use only first 6 pages)

